name: ERA_08
description:
Trained with the intent of producing realism but ended up with more of a stylized realism instead.

It's title is ERA_08 as it's the eighth era of training the model. I actually got up to 16, but found I kept coming back to this generation of the model for the results it produced. I still have a lot to learn, evidently.

I quite literally went out and bought a 4090 for the purposes of training my own models, so I hope you all enjoy the results.

Get interesting with your prompts! I purposefully avoided negative prompting Textual Inversions since I find them to limit results.

All images were upscaled 2x with the latent upscaler with a denoising strength of 0.6.
